function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
-- Turn off thumping
	bCabinetChecked = true
-- Bats fly out of the cabinet
	local moveLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(actorBat)[1]
	local moveLoc2 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(actorBat2)[1]
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(actorCabinetFX, fxImpactWood)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorBat)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorBat2)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(powerPassability, "MAIN", actorBat)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(powerPassability, "MAIN", actorBat2)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(actorBat, moveLoc, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(actorBat, 2.0)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(actorBat2, moveLoc2, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(actorBat2, 2.0)
end

function Start(flGameTime)
	if not (bCabinetChecked) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySound(actorCabinetFX, soundThud)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
-- Lorath moves into the chapel
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convLorath01, actorLorath) 	-- Lorath to horse
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorLorath)
	Hydra.QActorSetConversationStatus(actorLorath, false)
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorLorath, 0.5)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorLorath, locLorathInChapel, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorSetConversationStatus(actorLorath, true)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convLorath02, actorLorath) 	-- Lorath "she's not here..."
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(actorLorath, "LorathInChapel")
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	Hydra.ActorSetSheathPreference(actorLorath, 2)

end

unk_9c63f9d.value:
-- Lorath moves out
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorLorath, locLorathConfront, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(actorLorath, "InPosition")
-- Iosef and Knights Arrive
local tPaleKnights = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("EpiloguePaleKnights")
for i, idActor in ipairs(tPaleKnights) do
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idActor)
	local moveLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idActor)[1]
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActor, moveLoc, "NPC_WALK", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActor, moveLoc)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(idActor, "InPosition")
end

Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorLorath)
Hydra.QActorEnableAI(actorLorath, true)

local tPaleKnights = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("EpiloguePaleKnights")
for i, idActor in ipairs(tPaleKnights) do
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(idActor)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idActor, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActor, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetCannotBeTargetedByAI(idActor, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetNeverDie(idActor, false)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActor)
	Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idActor, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
end

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorIosef) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(actorIosef) then
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convIosef03, actorIosef)
end
